inside the bathroom,

01:10.900 --> 01:12.100
it's kind of interesting.

01:12.133 --> 01:15.067
I just observed a subject
leave a vehicle here,

01:15.067 --> 01:16.267
and he picked something up,

01:16.300 --> 01:18.600
and he kinda got behind
a propane tank display rack.

01:18.633 --> 01:21.267
It's suspicious, so we're just
gonna do a little follow-up

01:21.300 --> 01:22.367
